<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-7">
    <h1><%= current_page.data.title %></h1>

    <p>DSK International is easily accessible by car or train (Rokko Liner, Island Center Station), approximately 20 minutes from Sannomiya (Kobe's down-town area) and 35 minutes from Umeda (Osaka's down-town area).</p>

    <h2>Enrolment Enquiries</h2>

    <p>Please email <%= mail_to data.config.contact.mailto, data.config.contact.mailto %>
      or call <strong>+81 <a href="tel:078 857 9777">(0)78-857-9777</a></strong>
      to speak to one of our office staff about enrolments.</p>
    <p>Please visit our <%= link_to 'Admissions', local_path('admissions') %> section of the website for further details.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">College Tours</h2>

    <p>DSK International offers guided School tours providing an insight into the school on a normal school day.</p>
    <p>Bookings are required for a school tour and we kindly ask you make your booking below:</p>
    <p><%= mail_to data.config.contact.mailto + '?subject=School Tour', 'Book a tour »', class: 'btn btn-lg btn-info', role: 'button' %></p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">Open Events</h2>

    <p>Our Open Events provide a fun and unique opportunity to spend time with current students, parents, teachers and staff. We have a variety of open events happening at our school and attendance is free and bookings usually aren't required. Please see a list of our <%= link_to 'events here', local_path('news') %>.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">Open Days</h2>

    <p>Our school has two open days every year: one in March and one in November. This is one of the best opportunities to come and explore our school, meet the staff and get a sense for what life is like at DSKI. Details of the next open day will be available on the <%= link_to 'events page', local_path('news') %> very soon. If you are interested in booking your place at the open day please contact us here:</p>
    <p><%= mail_to data.config.contact.mailto + '?Subject=Open Day', 'Open Day Enquiry »', class: 'btn btn-lg btn-info', role: 'button' %></p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">General Enquiries</h2>

    <p>If you have any other enquiries or questions about our school please get in touch anytime. You can contact us about anything by email</p>
    <p class="mb-5"><%= mail_to data.config.contact.mailto + '?Subject=General Enquiry', 'General Enquiry »', class: 'btn btn-lg btn-info', role: 'button' %></p>
  </div>

